"emphasis>) permission allows owner to examine contents of the file."
msgstr ""
"la permission en <emphasis role=\"strong\">lecture</emphasis> (<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">r</emphasis>) permet à son propriétaire de voir le contenu "
"du fichier&nbsp;;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">write</emphasis> (<emphasis role=\"strong\">w</"
