"manvolnum></citerefentry> command to change timestamps of existing files."
msgstr ""
"Utilisez la commande <citerefentry><refentrytitle>touch</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry> pour modifier "
"l’horodatage des fichiers existants."

