#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Official documentations for NM and Wicd on Debian are provided in "
"\"<literal>/usr/share/doc/network-manager/README.Debian</literal>\" and "
"\"<literal>/usr/share/doc/wicd/README.Debian</literal>\", respectively."
msgstr ""
"Les documentations officielles de NM et Wicd sous Debian sont fournies "
"respectivement par «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/doc/network-manager/README."
"Debian</literal>&nbsp;» et «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/doc/wicd/README."
"Debian</literal>&nbsp;»."

