msgid "Sharing, copying, and archiving"
msgstr "Partager, copier et archiver"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><para>
msgid ""
"The security of the data and its controlled sharing have several aspects."
msgstr ""
"La sécurité des données et leur partage contrôlé présentent plusieurs "
"aspects."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid "The creation of data archive"
msgstr "La création d'une archive des données"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid "The remote storage access"
msgstr "L’accès à un stockage distant"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid "The duplication"
msgstr "La duplication"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid "The tracking of the modification history"
msgstr "Le suivi de l’historique des modifications"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid "The facilitation of data sharing"
msgstr "La facilité de partager les données"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
msgid "The prevention of unauthorized file access"
msgstr "La prévention de l’accès non autorisé aux données"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
