#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"Then the blank CD-R is inserted to the CD drive, and the ISO9660 image file, "
"\"<literal>cd.iso</literal>\" is written to this device, e.g., \"<literal>/"
"dev/hda</literal>\", using <citerefentry><refentrytitle>wodim</"
"refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry> by the following."
msgstr ""
"Le CD-R vierge est alors inséré dans le graveur de CD et le fichier image "
"ISO9660 «&nbsp;<literal>cd.iso</literal>&nbsp;» est écrit vers le "
"périphérique, par exemple; «&nbsp;<literal>/dev/hda</literal>&nbsp;» en "
"utilisant <citerefentry><refentrytitle>wodim</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</"
"manvolnum></citerefentry> de la manière suivante&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
