#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"XML text looks somewhat like <ulink url=\"&html;\">HTML</ulink>.  It enables "
"us to manage multiple formats of output for a document.  One easy XML system "
"is the <literal>docbook-xsl</literal> package, which is used here."
msgstr ""
"Le texte en XML ressemble un peu à <ulink url=\"&html;\">HTML</ulink>. Il "
"vous permet de gérer de nombreux format de sortie pour un document. Un "
"système XML facile est le paquet <literal>docbook-xsl</literal> qui est "
"utilisé ici."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid "Each XML file starts with standard XML declaration as the following."
msgstr ""
"Chaque fichier XML commence par la déclaration XML standard suivante&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid "&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?&gt;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid "The basic syntax for one XML element is marked up as the following."
msgstr ""
"La syntaxe de base d'un élément XML est balisée de la manière suivante&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid "&lt;name attribute=\"value\"&gt;content&lt;/name&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;name attribute=\"value\"&gt;contenu&lt;/nom&gt;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"XML element with empty content is marked up in the following short form."
msgstr ""
"Un élément XML dont le contenu est vide est balisé de la façon raccourcie "
"suivante&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid "&lt;name attribute=\"value\"/&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;name attribute=\"value\"/&gt;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid ""
"The \"<literal>attribute=\"value\"</literal>\" in the above examples are "
"optional."
msgstr ""
"«&nbsp;<literal>attribute=\"value\"</literal>&nbsp;» dans les exemples ci-"
"dessus es optionnel."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
msgid "The comment section in XML is marked up as the following."
msgstr "L’action commentaire en XML est balisée comme suit&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#, no-wrap
msgid "&lt;!-- comment --&gt;"
msgstr "&lt;!-- comment --&gt;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><para>
